  <!-- ============================================================
       WeWeb consultant notes (delete before production):

       URL: portal.pbc.au/contacts

       PURPOSE
         Master directory across all projects. Distinct from the
         project-scoped Project Detail > Contacts tab. This page
         is the canonical entry point for managing contacts,
         companies, internal staff, and portal user accounts.

       FOUR TABS — DATA SOURCES
         1. Clients
            - View: v_clients
            - Source: public.contacts filtered to those linked via
              project_contacts with stakeholder_category = client_owner,
              UNION contacts holding a portal user record with role=client
            - Returns: contact_id, full_name, position, company_id,
              company_name, email, phone, mobile, portal_user_status,
              active_projects_count, last_contacted_at

         2. Companies
            - View: v_companies
            - Source: public.companies with aggregations
            - Returns: company_id, company_name, abn, company_type_code
              (FK to public.company_types.type_code), company_type_label
              (joined from company_types.display_label), company_type_badge
              (joined from company_types.badge_colour), status (active |
              archived | merged), activity_state (active | dormant —
              derived: dormant = no project activity in 12 months),
              is_debtor (boolean — derived: debtor_projects_count > 0),
              contacts_count, active_projects_count, debtor_projects_count,
              last_activity_at
            - company_type is a LOOKUP not an enum (per CN-2026-002).
              New types added via Settings › Company types admin page.
              No code or migration required to add new types.
            - builder = head contractor / construction company. contractor
              = subbies and trade contractors (electrical, structural
              steel, AV/security, scaffolding). Additional types can be
              added through the admin UI as needed (e.g. solar installer,
              hydraulic contractor, ESD consultant).

         3. Staff
            - View: v_staff
            - Source: public.staff joined to public.users
            - Returns: staff_id, full_name, title (free text, display only),
              role (LOCKED ENUM: Director | Certifier | Surveyor |
              Engineer | Inspector | Manager | Admin — drives portal
              permissions, capacity reports, and signing authority),
              registrations (jsonb array of {type, number, jurisdiction}),
              office, email, phone, status (active | leave | inactive),
              project_allocations_count
            - Registrations stored as jsonb — supports multiple per
              staff member (Duncan: NT 19209BU + NT 19209ES)
            - title is cosmetic only (e.g. "Senior Building Certifier")
              and does NOT control any permission. All permission logic
              keys off role.

         4. All Portal Users
            - View: v_portal_users
            - Source: public.users joined to auth.users
            - Returns: user_id, full_name, role enum (admin | manager |
              staff | client | consultant), linked_entity_type (staff |
              contact), linked_entity_id, email, status (active | invited
              | disabled | suspended), last_sign_in_at, mfa_enabled

       CROSS-TAB PIVOTS
         - Clients tab → click company name → opens Companies tab
           filtered to that company_id
         - Companies tab → click contacts count → opens Clients tab
           filtered to that company_id
         - Companies tab → click projects count → opens Projects list
           filtered to that company_id
         - Portal Users tab → click linked entity → opens corresponding
           tab (Staff or Clients) and scrolls/highlights the row

       ROLE GATES
         Clients tab:
           - View       — any staff
           - Add        — Admin, Manager
           - Edit       — Admin, Manager
           - Archive    — Admin only (soft delete)
         Companies tab:
           - View       — any staff
           - Add        — Admin, Manager
           - Edit       — Admin, Manager
           - Merge      — Admin only (when duplicates detected)
         Staff tab:
           - View       — any staff
           - Add/Edit   — Admin only (creates auth.users + staff +
                          public.users in transaction)
           - Status change — Admin only
         All Portal Users tab:
           - View       — Admin, Manager
           - Invite     — Admin, Manager
           - Disable    — Admin only
           - Reset MFA  — Admin only

       BULK ACTIONS
         Export   — all tabs, ADMIN ONLY
                    Default format XLSX (preserves ABN leading zeros
                    and date formatting). CSV available via dropdown.
                    Every export writes an audit row: user_id, tab,
                    filter state, format, row count, timestamp.
         Bulk email and bulk portal invite are NOT supported. Clients are
         invited individually at the point of creation. Bulk delete is
         NOT supported on any tab — contacts may carry audit-relevant
         history.

       SEARCH
         Each tab has its own search input scoped to that tab's data.
         The global top-bar search covers all tabs simultaneously and
         deep-links to the matching row.

       PAGE PROTECTION
         Staff-only page. Clients access their own contact details via
         a different "My profile" page on the client side; the master
         directory is not exposed to clients.
       ============================================================ -->

  <style type="text/tailwindcss">
    @theme {
      --color-primary-100: #E8EBF2;
      --color-primary-500: #071D49;
      --color-primary-700: #1A3A7A;
      --color-primary-900: #040F26;

      --color-neutral-100: #F8F9FA;
      --color-neutral-200: #E9ECEF;
      --color-neutral-300: #DEE2E6;
      --color-neutral-500: #ADB5BD;
      --color-neutral-600: #6C757D;
      --color-neutral-700: #495057;
      --color-neutral-800: #343A40;

      --color-success: #1A7A4A;
      --color-success-light: #D4EDDA;
      --color-warning: #B45309;
      --color-warning-light: #FFF3CD;
      --color-danger: #B91C1C;
      --color-danger-light: #F8D7DA;
      --color-info: #1D4ED8;
      --color-info-light: #DBEAFE;
      --color-pending: #C2410C;
      --color-pending-light: #FFEDD5;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: var(--color-neutral-800);
      background: var(--color-neutral-100);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      font-feature-settings: "tnum";
    }

    @layer components {
      .btn {
        @apply inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-medium text-[13px] leading-none
               px-4 py-2 rounded-[6px] transition-colors duration-150
               focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2;
      }
      .btn-primary    { @apply bg-primary-500 text-white hover:bg-primary-700 active:bg-primary-900; }
      .btn-secondary  { @apply bg-white text-primary-500 border border-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-100; }
      .btn-ghost      { @apply bg-transparent text-neutral-600 hover:bg-neutral-100 hover:text-neutral-800; }

      .badge {
        @apply inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-[4px] text-[10px] font-semibold leading-tight whitespace-nowrap uppercase tracking-wider;
      }

      /* Portal status */
      .badge-portal-active  { @apply bg-success-light text-success; }
      .badge-portal-invited { @apply bg-warning-light text-warning; }
      .badge-portal-none    { @apply bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-500; }

      /* Company type */
      .badge-comp-client       { @apply bg-primary-100 text-primary-500; }
      .badge-comp-builder      { @apply bg-pending-light text-pending; }
      .badge-comp-design       { @apply bg-info-light text-info; }
      .badge-comp-consultancy  { @apply bg-warning-light text-warning; }
      .badge-comp-authority    { @apply bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-700; }
      .badge-comp-contractor   { @apply bg-success-light text-success; }

      /* Role badge */
      .badge-role-admin      { @apply bg-danger-light text-danger; }
      .badge-role-manager    { @apply bg-warning-light text-warning; }
      .badge-role-staff      { @apply bg-info-light text-info; }
      .badge-role-client     { @apply bg-primary-100 text-primary-500; }
      .badge-role-consultant { @apply bg-success-light text-success; }

      /* User status */
      .badge-user-active     { @apply bg-success-light text-success; }
      .badge-user-invited    { @apply bg-warning-light text-warning; }
      .badge-user-disabled   { @apply bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-600; }
      .badge-user-suspended  { @apply bg-danger-light text-danger; }

      /* Staff status */
      .badge-staff-active   { @apply bg-success-light text-success; }
      .badge-staff-leave    { @apply bg-warning-light text-warning; }
      .badge-staff-inactive { @apply bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-600; }

      /* Sidebar nav */
      .nav-item {
        @apply flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 text-[13px] text-white/70 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white
               transition-colors duration-100 border-l-[3px] border-transparent -ml-[3px];
      }
      .nav-item-active {
        @apply text-white bg-white/[0.06] border-white font-medium;
      }
      .nav-section-label {
        @apply px-5 py-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-white/40 font-semibold;
      }

      /* Page tab nav (top-level for this page) */
      .ptab-link {
        @apply px-4 py-3 text-[13px] text-neutral-600 hover:text-neutral-800 border-b-2 border-transparent
               whitespace-nowrap transition-colors duration-100 inline-flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer;
      }
      .ptab-link-active {
        @apply text-primary-500 border-primary-500 font-semibold;
      }
      .ptab-count {
        @apply text-[11px] bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-medium;
      }
      .ptab-link-active .ptab-count {
        @apply bg-primary-100 text-primary-500;
      }

      .card {
        @apply bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-[8px] shadow-[0_1px_3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)];
      }

      /* Data tables (shared across tabs) */
      .dir-table { @apply w-full text-[13px] text-neutral-800; }
      .dir-table thead th {
        @apply text-left px-3 py-2.5 text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-500
               bg-neutral-100 border-b border-neutral-200;
      }
      .dir-table thead th.text-right { @apply text-right; }
      .dir-table tbody td {
        @apply px-3 py-3 border-b border-neutral-200 align-middle;
      }
      .dir-table tbody td.text-right { @apply text-right; }
      .dir-table tbody tr {
        @apply hover:bg-neutral-100 transition-colors duration-100 cursor-pointer;
      }
      .dir-table tbody tr:last-child td {
        @apply border-b-0;
      }

      /* Contact avatar (Clients) */
      .ent-avatar {
        @apply w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary-100 text-primary-500 flex items-center justify-center
               text-[11px] font-semibold flex-shrink-0;
      }
      /* Company avatar (Companies) */
      .ent-avatar-company {
        @apply w-8 h-8 rounded bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-center
               text-[11px] font-semibold flex-shrink-0 border border-neutral-200;
      }
      /* Staff avatar (Staff) — distinct from Clients */
      .ent-avatar-staff {
        @apply w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center
               text-[11px] font-semibold flex-shrink-0;
      }

      /* Staff role badge (enum: drives portal permissions) */
      .badge-staff-role-director   { @apply bg-primary-100 text-primary-500; }
      .badge-staff-role-certifier  { @apply bg-info-light text-info; }
      .badge-staff-role-surveyor   { @apply bg-info-light text-info; }
      .badge-staff-role-engineer   { @apply bg-success-light text-success; }
      .badge-staff-role-inspector  { @apply bg-pending-light text-pending; }
      .badge-staff-role-manager    { @apply bg-warning-light text-warning; }
      .badge-staff-role-admin      { @apply bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-700; }

      /* MFA plain text (replaces badge — less visually competitive with Status) */
      .mfa-on    { @apply text-[12px] font-medium text-success; }
      .mfa-off   { @apply text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-500; }
      .mfa-none  { @apply text-[12px] text-neutral-400; }

      /* Inline link */
      .pivot-link {
        @apply text-primary-500 hover:underline cursor-pointer;
      }

      /* Filter chip */
      .chip {
        @apply inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2.5 py-1 text-[12px] font-medium
               bg-white border border-neutral-300 text-neutral-700 rounded-[20px]
               hover:border-neutral-500 transition-colors cursor-pointer;
      }
      .chip-active {
        @apply bg-primary-100 text-primary-500 border-primary-500;
      }

      /* Icon button */
      .icon-btn {
        @apply inline-flex items-center justify-center w-7 h-7 rounded-[4px] text-neutral-500
               hover:bg-neutral-200 hover:text-neutral-800 transition-colors;
      }

      /* Registration pill */
      .reg-pill {
        @apply inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-mono font-semibold
               bg-primary-100 text-primary-500;
      }

      /* Linked entity small chip (portal users tab) */
      .link-small {
        @apply inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-medium
               bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-700 hover:bg-primary-100 hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors cursor-pointer;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

